requires python jsonpath module:
        sudo apt-get install pyton-pip
        pip install jsonpath-rw


installing nltk:

1. wget https://bootstrap.pypa.io/ez_setup.py -O - | sudo python
2. sudo easy_install pip
3. sudo pip install -U numpy (optional)
4. sudo pip install -U nltk


required files:
1. etc/pos/<any_name>.txt : phrases most distinctively summarizing wellness of your application (e.g. INFO logs, startup logs etc.)
2. etc/neg/<any_name>.txt : phrases summarizing downward trends, critical states etc. (e.g. ERROR/FATAL logs, possible runtime errors)



                      